Title: Urban Decay Revolution Lipstick 2.8 g(Anarchy)
Description: The best of both worlds, Sheer Revolution Lipstick is everything you love about the original Revolution Lipstickwith a sheer, shiny finish. The formula is laced with Maxi-Lip (which defines and hydrates lips while making them look plumper and fuller), along with a nourishing blend of oils and antioxidants. Shea butter and jojoba, olive and babassu oils moisturize and condition, while vitamin C and vitamin E provide a hit of antioxidants. We put this formula in our cool, custom-designed lipstick component; to set this sheer formula apart, we made the case light purple (instead of gunmetal like our traditional Revolution Lipstick case). Organically shaped facets make the case feel amazing in your hand; Urban Decay is debossed on the side of the lid, with UD debossed on the top of the cap. For bolder color and ultra long wear, first line the outside of lips with 24/7 Glide-On Lip Pencil in Ozone (our clear shade) to fill in any fine lines and prevent feathering. Next, fill in lips completely with 24/7 Glide-On Lip Pencil in a shade that matches the Sheer Revolution Lipstick shade you'll be using. This will define lips, intensify color and provide even longer wear. Follow with Sheer Revolution Lipstick.
